        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl0_Label1"><p>October 3, 2013 Iperius Backup 3.1 introduces several important features. Now from the Web Console you can perform a backup on the machine where Iperius is installed . You can launch without problems one or more backup jobs with a single click. Furthermore, you can also launch the Iperius AutoUpdate. You will no longer need [&hellip;]</p>
