            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl3_Label1"><p>The following tutorial shows how to create a Dropbox App in the App Console, to get an authentication token needed by Iperius to authenticate and make a remote backup on Dropbox. First of all, access your account, specifically in the reserved area where you can configure an App, from this address: https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps/create Set the various options like [&hellip;]</p>
