        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl4_Label1"><p>Iperius is a powerful and complete backup software that allows OneDrive backup and cloud backup on all major storage platforms: Google Drive, OneDrive for Business, Amazon S3, Azure Storage and Dropbox. With this simple tutorial we&#8217;re going to see how to enable the OneDrive API and get the Client ID code (App ID) to perform [&hellip;]</p>
