        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl6_Label1"><p>Iperius Backup is a reliable FTP backup software and a perfect solution to save your data remotely. It is possible to configure online backups to any FTP or SFTP server, even simultaneously, with bandwidth limitation and advanced filters. Iperius can make incremental backups: while the first time all files are copied to the destination, the other [&hellip;]</p>
