        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl7_Label1"><p>Iperius Backup is a powerful and reliable software to save your data remotely. It easily allows to make online backups to any remote server, even in parallel mode, with advanced features like bandwidth limitation and secure protocols such as FTPS and SFTP. Iperius is also provided with an professional and dedicated online backup service: Iperius Online [&hellip;]</p>
