        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl8_Label1"><p>Iperius is a very flexible backup software, that also allows to backup WordPress websites and MySQL databases. With a very simple configuration it can download entire websites and export any MySQL database. This feature is available in the Advanced Database edition. The website is downloaded in incremental mode (only new or changed files are downloaded and [&hellip;]</p>
